sec.p:
The second parameter represents the affinity coefficient between the adsorptive material and the adsorbed compound, determined from the Toth (
b T
) and Langmuir ($b$) isotherms. The higher the affinity coefficient value, the stronger the affinity. The affinity coefficient values obtained were 0.124 L mg-1 for the Toth isotherm and 0.051 L mg-1 for the Langmuir isotherm.
